uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.servlet

Class MultiPartServletService

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.servlet.DefaultServletService
      • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.servlet.MultiPartServletService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AppContextCleanup, AppContextService<ServletService>, Contexed, ServletService

    public class MultiPartServletService
extends DefaultServletService
implements ServletService
    A ServletService that supports MultiPart form content via tha apache fileupload libraries. It will therefore work in a servlet 2 container. For servlet 3 there are equivalent methods in httprequest and we can remove this dependency by using that
    See Also:
    Servlet3MultiPartServletService, FileUploadWebappContextListener
